Package: suezalla
Title: Custom ggplot2 Themes and Colour Palettes for Stylized Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Susan", "Canavan", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    The suezalla package provides lightweight, expressive tools for visual storytelling 
    with ggplot2. It includes several curated colour palettes and themes, including 
    minimal designs, vintage styles, and a playful zombie theme. Use it to create 
    clean or stylized plots with ease, consistent branding, and beautiful defaults.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
